ok it took me a while to get this working so here goes I hope this can help. 

Once you are done downloading the torrent you need to get a program called WinISO. WinISO is a program that costs 30$ to register but you can find a crack for it on astalavista.box.sk, the crack I used for WinISO is called WinISO_5.3_Loader_By_F_Cruger and it worked.

Once you do that, use win ISO to extract nsz-aip9a.BIN and nsz-aip9b.BIN each to their own folder.

Then in the folder where you extracted nsz-aip9a.BIN, run "setup.exe"

When you install it, if it asks you for a serial number, use 400-12345678, which is the number located in the txt file in the crack folder.

When you run the program, you will get a window asking you to register by entering an activation code. To get the activation code, you use the pdx-aip9.exe program that is in the folder called crack. 

In pdx-aip9.exe, type in the request code that you see on the autodesk window, and pdx-aip9.exe will give you a code to put back into inventor. Select Germany as the registration country and it should work for you, as it has for me. 

Thanks alot to the guy who shared this!
